data.description: Absolutely stunning 5-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom home in Anderson Creek Club! This 2771 sqft residence boasts elegance and functionality. Step onto the covered front porch and enter a world of hardwood flooring throughout the first level. The kitchen is a dream with granite countertops, a spacious island, a breakfast nook, and an ample amount of cabinet and countertop space to provide convenience. A dedicated office space and formal dining room on the main floor add versatility The primary bathroom features a beautiful tiled shower, and all bedrooms are located upstairs for privacy. Enjoy outdoor living with a sliding glass door leading to a covered back patio and deck. With a 2-car garage, this home is a perfect blend of luxury and practicality. Welcome to your dream home!
